<body>
<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>

<p><rs type="material" key="marmor">White marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">statue base</rs> with moulding (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">1.48</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.40</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.90</measure>). The inscription must have begun on an upper feature, now lost, but fragments of the statuary have been found. There is a hole cut through the lower moulding for a water pipe.</p></div><div type="description" n="text"><head>Description of Text</head><p> Inscribed on upper moulding which is chipped at right.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>Elaborately serifed letters; l.1, <measure dim="none">0.03-0.035</measure>; l.2, <measure dim="none">0.0253</measure>; l.3, <measure dim="none">0.02-0.025</measure>.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date cert="low" notAfter="0100" notBefore="0001" exact="none">First century A.D.</date>
cf. <rs type="criteria">lettering</rs> of <xref type="iAph">1282</xref> (=MAMA 449)</p>
</div>
<div type="edition" lang="grc">
<head lang="en">Edition</head>
<ab><lb n="0"/><gap extent="unknown" dim="left" reason="lost" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost"><w lemma="ὁ">ὁ</w> <w>δεῖνα</w> <w lemma="κατά">κατὰ</w> <w lemma="ὁ">τὴν</w> <w lemma="ὁ">τοῦ</w> <w lemma="δεῖνα">δεῖνος</w></supplied>  <w><supplied reason="lost">δια</supplied><lb n="1" type="worddiv"/>ταγὴν</w> <w lemma="ὁ">τὸν</w> <persName type="divine" full="yes">Ἡρακλέα</persName> <w lemma="καί">καὶ</w> <w lemma="ὁ">τὸν</w> <persName type="divine" full="yes">Τρείτωνα</persName> <w lemma="καί">καὶ</w> <w lemma="ὁ">τὸν</w> <orig n="unresolved">λ</orig><gap extent="6" dim="right" reason="lost" unit="character"/><lb n="2"/> <w lemma="ἀνατίθημι">ἀνέθηκεν</w> <w lemma="ἐκ">ἐκ</w> <w lemma="ὁ">τῶν</w> <w>ἰδίων</w> <w lemma="καί">καὶ</w> <w lemma="ὁ">τὰ</w> <w>σωληνοθετήμ<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">ατα</supplied></w><lb n="3"/> <w lemma="καί">καὶ</w> <w lemma="ὁ">τὰ</w> <w>ὕδατα</w> <w lemma="εἰς">εἰς</w> <sic n="superfluous"><orig n="unresolved">σ</orig></sic> <w lemma="ὁ">τὸ</w> <w>βαλανεῖον</w> <w lemma="πᾶς">πάντα</w> <space unit="character" extent="7" dim="horizontal"/></ab>
</div>


<div type="translation">
<head>Translation</head>
<p><gap extent="unknown" dim="left" reason="lost" unit="character"/> <supplied reason="lost">according to the</supplied> command <supplied reason="lost">of a deity whose name has been lost</supplied> set up the Herakles and the Triton and the L<gap extent="unknown" dim="internal" reason="lost" unit="character"/> at his own expense and the channelling and all the water for the Bath.</p>
</div>
